data.title: Aaron Carter- "I Want Candy" (Remix)
data.text:
Post by YourFaveIsAFlop on

You know, if somebody else did this, i could see it being a minor hit if you got like cardi b on it

Post by Deleted on

"She's got everything that i desire."

Maybe I'd appreciate this more - and find it far more interesting - if he kept the original "he" lyrics. At least for one of the verses.

It's not terrible. I think what made the original work really well is the exaggerated production and vibrant vocal. This comes off like some random and fairly bland YouTube cover.

Anyway... nice True Blue tribute on the cover art.

Post by Harx on

@mello said:

"She's got everything that i desire."

Maybe I'd appreciate this more - and find it far more interesting - if he kept the original "he" lyrics. At least for one of the verses.

Actual original version from the 60s has "she" in the lyrics.
